      <title>以色列在威脅入侵前加強對加沙拉法的打擊</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-intensifies-strikes-gazas-rafah-ahead-threatened-invasion-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，醫務人員表示，以色列連夜加強了對拉法的空襲，造成至少六名巴勒斯坦人死亡。可能會造成大規模人員傷亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-intensifies-strikes-gazas-rafah-ahead-threatened-invasion-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
