      <title>安全官員稱，伊拉克在最近的大規模處決中絞死了11名被判犯有恐怖主義罪的人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-hangs-11-convicted-terrorism-latest-mass-executions-security-officials-say-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[當地安全官員週四表示，伊拉克絞死了 11 名因恐怖主義罪名被判處死刑的武裝分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-hangs-11-convicted-terrorism-latest-mass-executions-security-officials-say-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:21:06 GMT</pubDate>
